column1:
School Identification
(this section is used for unique identification of school. In some cases they also could be used for clasterisation. School Name could be missed, in this case schools will receive automatic names during the data import (f.e. School #1, School #2 etc.), but you could not miss all three fields)
column5:
Geographical Location and Infrastructure Presence
(this section is used by methodology of connecting schools to broadband transport backbones (Middle-Mile))
column10:
Users
(this section is used for calculation number of devices that will be used in school)
column17:
Building
(this section is used by LAN methodology for calculating CAPEX & OPEX for school LAN & Hotspot)
column35:
Data entering completeness
(this section is used for demonstrating if it is all necessary information was intered for particular school (in the row) for future processing and caclulations)
